HEADWORD: Absonant
<hw>Ab"so*nant</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>ab</ets>
+ <ets>sonans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>sonare</ets> to sound.]</ety>
<def>Discordant; contrary; -- opposed to <ant>consonant</ant>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Absonant</xex> to nature.⟦rdquo⟧
